WEBVTT

01:42.960 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:49.009
[Episode 15]

01:54.970 --> 01:55.650
Why're you here?

01:56.470 --> 01:57.580
I knew you'd be here.

01:58.280 --> 02:00.100
I happened to be shooting near the office.

02:00.900 --> 02:01.750
Haven't eaten yet, yeah?

02:03.790 --> 02:04.960
Where are your manager and assistant?

02:05.070 --> 02:06.020
Why are you alone?

02:06.710 --> 02:08.150
I'm not that popular.

02:08.229 --> 02:08.949
It's more convenient

02:08.949 --> 02:09.630
alone.

02:11.100 --> 02:12.820
It's newly opened nearby.

02:13.030 --> 02:13.930
I tried it

02:13.950 --> 02:14.880
last week.

02:14.910 --> 02:15.660
It's quite good.

02:21.829 --> 02:22.829
It is quite good.

02:25.680 --> 02:26.340
By the way,

02:27.280 --> 02:28.300
you said you'd

02:28.340 --> 02:29.550
find me a professional.

02:29.590 --> 02:30.660
How's it going?

02:32.750 --> 02:33.400
There are

02:33.430 --> 02:34.430
two new scripts for you

02:34.660 --> 02:35.530
for the leading role.

02:35.870 --> 02:37.110
Must you do the previous one?

02:37.470 --> 02:38.240
You've sent me

02:38.270 --> 02:39.390
those two scripts.

02:40.910 --> 02:41.750
What's the difference

02:41.790 --> 02:42.710
from my previous roles?

02:44.380 --> 02:45.680
I'm not interested at all.

02:46.900 --> 02:48.270
With your current popularity,

02:48.829 --> 02:50.040
if you spend a few months

02:50.070 --> 02:50.760
to study

02:50.790 --> 02:52.200
and another year to shoot this film,

02:52.220 --> 02:53.670
when you return,

02:53.870 --> 02:54.700
you might not

02:54.829 --> 02:55.870
be as popular anymore.

02:56.190 --> 02:57.190
You should know

02:57.190 --> 02:58.670
what I've always wanted.

02:58.800 --> 03:00.160
I just want to play

03:00.190 --> 03:01.950
a role that's memorable.

03:02.950 --> 03:05.030
You said you'd support me.

03:05.030 --> 03:06.030
What's with this attitude?

03:12.550 --> 03:13.610
Alright.

03:14.190 --> 03:15.910
I've gone to Ninghai Police Academy

03:15.910 --> 03:16.930
to consult their principal.

03:17.470 --> 03:18.510
He found you a professor

03:18.510 --> 03:19.400
specializing

03:19.430 --> 03:20.980
in criminal psychology.

03:21.280 --> 03:22.370
You can start class tomorrow.

03:22.960 --> 03:23.780
Really?

03:26.590 --> 03:27.940
You were teasing me?

03:28.880 --> 03:29.500
Thank you.

03:29.950 --> 03:31.160
I'll go there tomorrow

03:31.190 --> 03:31.790
and learn

03:31.829 --> 03:32.390
earnestly.

03:33.350 --> 03:33.750
Hey.

03:34.870 --> 03:35.360
Let's drink.

03:36.030 --> 03:36.750
Okay. Let's celebrate.

03:38.790 --> 03:40.610
Today, I want to thank my boss.

03:44.030 --> 03:44.910
Boss, thank you

03:45.750 --> 03:46.700
for agreeing

03:47.070 --> 03:48.450
to that role for me.

03:57.760 --> 03:58.300
Eat up.

03:58.329 --> 03:59.350
Stop working.

03:59.630 --> 04:00.240
You are

04:00.270 --> 04:01.110
working way too much.

04:01.110 --> 04:01.870
Relax a bit.

04:26.790 --> 04:27.270
Hello?

04:27.790 --> 04:28.930
Are you home?

04:29.310 --> 04:29.930
Yeah.

04:30.710 --> 04:31.790
Okay, come downstairs.

04:31.830 --> 04:33.050
Tang Jie and I will be there soon.

04:33.670 --> 04:34.330
For what?

04:34.630 --> 04:36.640
I brought you some daily necessities,

04:36.750 --> 04:37.810
bowls and utensils.

04:37.870 --> 04:38.710
You have nothing.

04:38.710 --> 04:39.510
You'll starve to death.

04:40.790 --> 04:41.470
I don't need those.

04:41.710 --> 04:42.700
What do you mean?

04:43.030 --> 04:44.300
It's all free.

04:44.590 --> 04:45.070
Listen.

04:45.070 --> 04:45.880
This pot is great.

04:45.909 --> 04:46.909
It’s from Tang Jie’s client.

04:46.950 --> 04:48.650
We couldn't even bear to use it.

04:51.270 --> 04:53.020
You didn't tell Lu Yan that you came, did you?

04:53.630 --> 04:56.060
Don’t worry. Our lips are sealed.

04:56.390 --> 04:57.200
Cut the crap.

04:57.230 --> 04:57.720
Come down now.

04:57.750 --> 04:58.420
We're almost there.

04:58.670 --> 04:59.560
Okay.

05:02.630 --> 05:04.240
What's up with Jiang Chengyi?

05:04.270 --> 05:05.440
If he wants to protect her,

05:05.470 --> 05:06.510
why must he hide it?

05:06.630 --> 05:07.630
So wishy-washy.

05:07.670 --> 05:08.340
Gosh.

05:08.550 --> 05:10.150
Isn't Lu Yan the same?

05:14.190 --> 05:14.930
Hurry up.

05:16.630 --> 05:17.640
Why are you rushing me?

05:17.740 --> 05:19.530
Why don't you help me, huh?

05:20.510 --> 05:20.830
What?

05:20.830 --> 05:21.920
You want my wife to help?

05:21.950 --> 05:23.150
My pot's quite heavy.

05:23.230 --> 05:24.310
I'm helping!

05:24.670 --> 05:25.700
Don't tire yourselves out.

05:28.070 --> 05:29.130
Tang Jie, Zhong.

05:30.830 --> 05:31.430
I’ll leave first.

05:31.450 --> 05:31.970
Bye.

05:36.630 --> 05:37.640
Who was that?

05:38.750 --> 05:39.750
Who?

05:40.020 --> 05:41.020
It's just us two.

05:43.560 --> 05:44.760
Why are you two here?

05:44.930 --> 05:45.480
We...

05:46.730 --> 05:47.159
Honey.

05:47.190 --> 05:48.380
W-What are we doing here?

05:48.600 --> 05:49.180
We...

05:50.250 --> 05:52.540
We're here for hotpot!

05:52.750 --> 05:54.250
Hotpot?

05:55.080 --> 05:55.800
But I

05:55.830 --> 05:57.250
have a pot at home.

05:57.340 --> 05:57.940
Um...

05:58.510 --> 05:59.690
I don't eat the spicy broth.

05:59.790 --> 06:00.740
Half-and-half.

06:01.500 --> 06:02.630
Did you bring the ingredients?

06:03.110 --> 06:03.750
Ingre—

06:03.770 --> 06:05.670
We'll just order it!

06:06.110 --> 06:06.870
It's fresher.

06:07.030 --> 06:07.690
Let's go.

06:07.830 --> 06:08.670
I'm starving.

06:08.830 --> 06:09.590
T-Then

06:09.710 --> 06:11.330
why didn't you text me first?

06:18.710 --> 06:20.070
Let me check...

06:21.200 --> 06:22.550
Almost here. Ten minutes left.

06:28.550 --> 06:30.050
Let's plug the pot in later.

06:30.710 --> 06:31.590
I've brought the extension cord.

06:31.610 --> 06:32.300
Okay.

06:40.680 --> 06:41.350
What's wrong?

06:42.010 --> 06:43.320
Sound-controlled lights.

06:49.340 --> 06:50.520
Did she see me?

06:51.500 --> 06:52.720
The slippers are there.

06:52.790 --> 06:53.310
Okay.

06:53.350 --> 06:54.070
Honey, hold this for me.

06:54.070 --> 06:54.430
Okay.

06:55.370 --> 06:56.400
I'll go get changed.

06:56.550 --> 06:57.159
Okay.

07:00.200 --> 07:01.530
I need some water.

07:01.790 --> 07:03.000
Did she see me?

07:04.710 --> 07:05.670
No.

07:05.910 --> 07:07.060
We're eating hotpot.

07:07.230 --> 07:08.040
Want to join?

07:09.430 --> 07:10.330
That's too much.

07:50.030 --> 07:50.750
What are you looking at?

07:51.830 --> 07:52.300
Nothing.

07:52.430 --> 07:53.330
I was admiring

07:53.510 --> 07:54.600
your flowers.

07:55.830 --> 07:56.600
Honey.

07:56.620 --> 07:57.720
Let's raise some too.

07:57.800 --> 07:58.590
No thanks.

07:59.820 --> 08:01.210
You've got a neighbor next door?

08:01.510 --> 08:02.870
Why's the light still on?

08:03.230 --> 08:04.360
I think they're new here.

08:04.380 --> 08:05.660
I haven't met them.

08:06.470 --> 08:07.230
Where's the pot?

08:07.330 --> 08:08.220
Here, here.

08:08.580 --> 08:09.570
Give it to me.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.490
There's some veggies here.

08:23.430 --> 08:24.580
Hotpot's the best.

08:24.850 --> 08:26.020
It's so yummy.

08:26.650 --> 08:27.870
It's because this pot is good.

08:27.890 --> 08:28.750
Right, honey?

08:35.490 --> 08:36.460
Cheers to

08:36.510 --> 08:37.340
this hotpot.

08:38.020 --> 08:38.710
I'm not drinking.

08:38.730 --> 08:39.960
I've to write my thesis later.

08:41.390 --> 08:42.450
Honey, drink with me.

08:42.669 --> 08:43.230
I'll pass too.

08:43.270 --> 08:44.610
Who'll drive if we both drink?

08:44.710 --> 08:45.640
You drink then.

08:45.720 --> 08:46.980
You drink.

08:48.390 --> 08:49.280
Let's toast

08:49.310 --> 08:49.840
with water.

08:49.870 --> 08:50.760
Cheers.

08:50.850 --> 08:51.520
Cheers.

08:55.850 --> 08:57.360
Why'd you two...

08:57.910 --> 08:59.110
come to have hotpot with me

08:59.150 --> 09:00.110
so suddenly?

09:01.840 --> 09:03.510
Huh? Why else?

09:03.750 --> 09:05.190
I saw that you've lost weight.

09:05.310 --> 09:06.180
Eat more meat

09:06.430 --> 09:07.040
for energy.

09:10.990 --> 09:12.410
I'm really happy

09:13.070 --> 09:14.440
to have you two here.

09:14.630 --> 09:15.680
Thank you.

09:19.420 --> 09:20.630
How've you been lately?

09:20.770 --> 09:21.800
What are you busy with?

09:23.640 --> 09:24.820
It's been good.

09:25.030 --> 09:25.750
Well...

09:25.840 --> 09:27.370
Go to and from work,

09:27.790 --> 09:28.910
busy with...

09:30.110 --> 09:31.650
with what I should be with.

09:33.960 --> 09:35.380
What about you and Jiang?

09:37.540 --> 09:38.800
You're drunk.

09:38.820 --> 09:39.460
I just...

09:40.270 --> 09:41.310
I haven't even had a sip.

09:48.690 --> 09:50.220
Why'd you open the window?

09:50.590 --> 09:51.530
It's so cold.

09:54.350 --> 09:54.880
Honey.

09:54.910 --> 09:55.910
Didn't you say I was drunk?

09:55.910 --> 09:56.810
I need some fresh air.

09:57.390 --> 09:58.790
Let's just eat. Ignore him.

09:59.910 --> 10:00.840
Here, I'll get you more.

10:00.990 --> 10:01.600
A quail egg.

10:01.630 --> 10:02.680
I like quail eggs.

10:05.030 --> 10:05.820
Ignore him.

10:05.860 --> 10:06.540
Okay.

10:06.910 --> 10:07.820
There's an egg here.

10:08.260 --> 10:08.800
Here.

10:09.420 --> 10:10.090
Thanks.

10:24.600 --> 10:25.340
Lu Yan.

10:27.150 --> 10:27.880
I don't really

10:27.910 --> 10:28.590
have a right to

10:28.590 --> 10:29.790
meddle in your business.

10:30.230 --> 10:31.360
But today,

10:31.510 --> 10:33.310
as Jiang Chengyi's longtime buddy,

10:33.550 --> 10:34.500
I've to ask you this.

10:35.850 --> 10:36.710
Do you want

10:36.750 --> 10:37.950
to be with Jiang or not?

10:47.030 --> 10:48.350
Actually, I know

10:48.470 --> 10:49.940
he's always been in your heart,

10:50.080 --> 10:52.250
just like how you've always been in his!

10:55.710 --> 10:56.650
I know.

10:57.870 --> 10:58.430
Lu Yan.

10:59.260 --> 11:00.740
I know you're sad.

11:01.150 --> 11:02.450
But for many things,

11:02.720 --> 11:03.830
he's really not at fault.

11:05.750 --> 11:06.640
I know.

11:06.670 --> 11:08.470
Then why're you ignoring him?

11:08.630 --> 11:09.110
Do you know

11:09.110 --> 11:09.620
he moved

11:09.620 --> 11:11.030
next door for you?

11:12.870 --> 11:13.950
Moved next door?

11:16.790 --> 11:17.720
H-Honey.

11:17.870 --> 11:19.630
D-Do you understand

11:19.650 --> 11:20.940
what I just said?

11:21.590 --> 11:22.250
That is,

11:23.190 --> 11:24.780
she's annoyed with Jiang!

11:25.380 --> 11:26.830
So Jiang can't see her,

11:26.870 --> 11:28.100
but he's worried about her,

11:28.310 --> 11:28.890
s-so...

11:29.110 --> 11:29.910
His heart...

11:31.510 --> 11:33.490
lives next door to Lu Yan.

11:36.320 --> 11:37.980
His heart moved in next door.

11:42.030 --> 11:42.580
I...

11:42.670 --> 11:44.030
You don't have to explain.

11:44.030 --> 11:44.910
I understand.

11:44.950 --> 11:45.690
I get it.

11:48.270 --> 11:49.320
Actually,

11:50.590 --> 11:51.350
I know...

11:52.830 --> 11:54.040
it's not his fault.

11:54.590 --> 11:55.910
I don't blame him either.

11:57.150 --> 11:58.220
It's just that...

11:59.150 --> 12:01.380
seeing him reminds me of the past.

12:02.350 --> 12:03.280
I'm worried

12:03.310 --> 12:05.280
my negativity will

12:05.960 --> 12:06.840
get to him too.

12:08.680 --> 12:10.270
We can't be together like normal.

12:11.790 --> 12:13.970
So it's better not to see each other.

12:14.830 --> 12:15.380
I...

12:16.380 --> 12:18.190
I need some time too.

12:21.430 --> 12:22.010
Yes.

12:22.500 --> 12:24.110
She needs some time!

12:25.670 --> 12:26.760
She needs time!

12:26.840 --> 12:28.240
It's okay! Take your time!

12:30.310 --> 12:30.900
I...

12:30.990 --> 12:32.250
I can hear you!

12:32.280 --> 12:33.530
Well, the window's open.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.190
I thought

12:34.300 --> 12:35.590
the wind might be too loud.

12:36.450 --> 12:37.590
I'll close the window.

12:37.640 --> 12:38.420
No, no!

12:39.480 --> 12:40.310
No, I’m drunk.

12:40.350 --> 12:41.430
-I need fresh air.
-Ventilation...

12:42.430 --> 12:43.360
Or your place will reek.

13:29.830 --> 13:31.060
You don't have to

13:31.270 --> 13:32.550
bear so many things alone.

13:33.880 --> 13:35.190
You can just tell him.

13:35.510 --> 13:36.190
Maybe he is

13:36.230 --> 13:37.430
willing to bear them with you.

13:40.150 --> 13:41.160
You can't blame yourself

13:41.190 --> 13:42.270
for every mistake.

13:42.910 --> 13:43.470
Got it?

13:44.720 --> 13:45.450
Go easy on yourself

13:46.790 --> 13:48.110
and on Jiang Chengyi.

13:49.970 --> 13:50.830
Don't punish yourself

13:50.870 --> 13:51.670
for the past.

13:59.790 --> 14:00.830
But actually...

14:02.790 --> 14:04.070
I've made progress.

14:04.710 --> 14:06.430
Lately, I've been

14:06.470 --> 14:07.970
trying to change.

14:08.590 --> 14:09.080
Don't worry.

14:10.390 --> 14:11.130
I...

14:11.200 --> 14:12.510
I'll be fine soon.

14:15.500 --> 14:17.240
I'm really happy to hear that.

14:18.470 --> 14:19.150
Lu Yan.

14:19.310 --> 14:20.280
As long as you

14:20.310 --> 14:21.340
don't forget that

14:21.390 --> 14:22.430
Jiang's never stopped

14:22.510 --> 14:23.350
loving you.

14:24.240 --> 14:24.890
Here.

14:25.990 --> 14:26.890
For Jiang,

14:27.230 --> 14:27.750
a toast to you.

14:31.430 --> 14:32.090
Cheers.

14:32.430 --> 14:32.870
Cheers!

14:32.910 --> 14:33.930
Toasting the air?

14:34.150 --> 14:35.430
It's the thought that counts.

14:35.590 --> 14:36.790
-I'll drink the air!
-Cheers to us too.

14:53.680 --> 14:55.290
Thank you, guys.

15:19.760 --> 15:20.450
You’re back.

15:20.850 --> 15:21.430
Captain Jiang.

15:21.670 --> 15:22.300
Captain Jiang.

15:23.060 --> 15:24.150
The technical department

15:24.190 --> 15:25.680
is sorting out Wang Qiang's case

15:25.710 --> 15:26.310
for

15:26.350 --> 15:26.960
submission.

15:27.110 --> 15:28.620
But something new cropped up.

15:28.840 --> 15:29.590
This user

15:29.890 --> 15:31.850
[Reply when you're free!]
[Where are you!]
[Reply!]

15:30.000 --> 15:31.070
has been contacting him

15:31.110 --> 15:32.200
since three days ago,

15:32.510 --> 15:33.800
initially asking about his day

15:33.830 --> 15:34.710
and for him to reply.

15:34.910 --> 15:36.030
Our tech thought they were

15:36.030 --> 15:36.720
just friends.

15:36.950 --> 15:38.290
But since last night,

15:38.390 --> 15:39.920
they've been looking for Wang Qiang

15:39.990 --> 15:41.030
anxiously.

15:41.270 --> 15:42.440
Did you find out who this is?

15:42.700 --> 15:43.350
Yes.

15:43.350 --> 15:44.600
From the back-end data,

15:44.630 --> 15:46.550
this person is Liu Yujie.

15:47.070 --> 15:48.000
Liu Yujie?

15:48.540 --> 15:50.150
What? You know them?

15:52.420 --> 15:53.730
Did you ask Wang Qiang about it?

15:53.790 --> 15:54.320
I asked,

15:54.360 --> 15:55.350
but he wouldn't cooperate,

15:55.630 --> 15:56.860
saying he has no idea.

15:59.040 --> 16:00.430
Find a way to ask them out.

16:01.450 --> 16:02.200
Got it.

16:08.350 --> 16:09.430
Jiang Chengyi.

16:09.020 --> 16:11.610
[Ding Jing]

16:09.550 --> 16:10.430
Our families are having dinner

16:10.470 --> 16:11.530
the day after tomorrow.

16:11.890 --> 16:13.130
Can you come pick me up?

16:16.670 --> 16:17.310
Sorry.

16:17.330 --> 16:18.270
It's not on the way.

16:18.430 --> 16:19.240
Jing!

16:26.750 --> 16:27.190
Okay.

16:27.540 --> 16:29.310
See you there directly then.

16:30.260 --> 16:30.990
Jing.

16:31.130 --> 16:31.780
Look.

16:31.810 --> 16:32.650
How about these two?

16:32.790 --> 16:34.080
I think they really suit you.

16:34.100 --> 16:35.200
And they're new designs.

16:36.990 --> 16:37.950
Not bad, Liu Yujie.

16:38.510 --> 16:40.020
Your taste has improved.

16:40.880 --> 16:42.690
It's not about my taste.

16:42.710 --> 16:44.090
It's because you're pretty,

16:44.120 --> 16:45.350
so you look good in everything.

16:45.710 --> 16:47.110
Our Jing is so beautiful.

16:47.130 --> 16:47.710
Jiang Chengyi

16:47.750 --> 16:49.310
will fall head over heels for you.

16:51.250 --> 16:51.760
Okay.

16:51.790 --> 16:53.420
I'll take these two you picked.

16:53.670 --> 16:54.430
Any other new designs

16:54.470 --> 16:55.320
I can check out?

16:55.350 --> 16:55.720
Sure.

16:55.750 --> 16:57.270
I'll bring them all to you.

17:03.120 --> 17:03.880
Jing.

17:03.990 --> 17:06.079
Why don't I tell Jiang Chengyi

17:06.109 --> 17:07.510
about you being stalked?

17:07.920 --> 17:09.170
You're in danger now.

17:09.230 --> 17:10.990
He'll come to protect you.

17:11.599 --> 17:13.040
Talk nonsense to Jiang Chengyi

17:13.069 --> 17:14.109
and I’ll rip your mouth off.

17:16.910 --> 17:18.540
Okay, I won't.

17:18.790 --> 17:20.640
Why are you so mad?

17:21.390 --> 17:22.510
Mad?

17:23.069 --> 17:24.800
Have you done what I asked you to do?

17:24.990 --> 17:25.800
Where's Wang Qiang?

17:26.579 --> 17:27.470
Where's the stun gun?

17:29.470 --> 17:30.000
Um,

17:30.030 --> 17:31.760
I've sent him many texts,

17:31.790 --> 17:32.910
but he hasn't replied.

17:33.150 --> 17:34.590
Don't you have legs?

17:34.910 --> 17:36.550
Can't you go to his house to find him?

17:37.750 --> 17:38.520
Liu Yujie.

17:38.750 --> 17:39.820
Do you know how much money

17:39.870 --> 17:40.990
Wang Qiang took from me?

17:42.880 --> 17:44.080
A-A-A lot?

17:45.790 --> 17:46.870
100,000,

17:47.470 --> 17:49.220
and I'm being conservative.

17:50.980 --> 17:52.810
S-So much?

17:52.830 --> 17:54.070
Tell Wang Qiang

17:54.990 --> 17:57.080
I didn't pay him for nothing.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.470
Rush him to hold up

17:58.790 --> 17:59.890
his end of the deal.

18:00.710 --> 18:01.350
Don’t worry.

18:02.830 --> 18:03.510
Yujie.

18:05.810 --> 18:06.810
You too.

18:20.510 --> 18:21.550
Let's meet tonight.

18:26.090 --> 18:27.520
In serial murders,

18:27.550 --> 18:30.060
the murderer is usually a power junkie,

18:30.200 --> 18:32.320
that is someone power hungry.

18:32.830 --> 18:33.950
These people

18:34.150 --> 18:36.310
are obsessed with power.

18:36.850 --> 18:38.150
In order to control

18:38.150 --> 18:39.310
people around them,

18:39.490 --> 18:41.000
they often hide

18:41.070 --> 18:41.990
important info

18:42.200 --> 18:44.320
to gain the upper hand

18:44.390 --> 18:45.330
and attention

18:45.590 --> 18:46.310
to satisfy

18:46.330 --> 18:47.840
their distorted sense of authority.

18:49.230 --> 18:49.900
Also,

18:50.150 --> 18:50.990
they have another

18:51.070 --> 18:52.670
typical characteristic.

18:52.690 --> 18:53.480
That is,

18:54.390 --> 18:55.460
being the manipulator.

18:55.990 --> 18:57.140
Manipulation.

18:58.000 --> 18:59.230
They'll repeatedly pretend

18:59.230 --> 19:00.530
to be vulnerable

19:00.870 --> 19:01.580
and helpless,

19:01.670 --> 19:03.170
and even pretend to please others.

19:03.680 --> 19:04.110
Ms. Yu

19:04.110 --> 19:05.390
is our criminal psychology expert

19:05.390 --> 19:06.750
in the Police Academy.

19:08.100 --> 19:09.310
Serial killers of

19:09.350 --> 19:10.030
civilized societies

19:10.050 --> 19:11.710
usually have such characteristics.

19:12.240 --> 19:13.510
They're very confusing.

19:13.550 --> 19:14.820
She was involved

19:15.080 --> 19:16.350
in many major cases.

19:16.990 --> 19:18.230
Manipulating others.

19:18.580 --> 19:19.150
They even

19:19.150 --> 19:19.990
misguide people

19:20.030 --> 19:20.990
around them

19:21.040 --> 19:22.230
to believe they're kind.

19:23.270 --> 19:24.200
So, as I was...

19:24.930 --> 19:26.070
What's the rush?

19:29.910 --> 19:30.730
Next week,

19:30.830 --> 19:31.670
submit a reflection

19:31.690 --> 19:33.270
on this class.

19:33.950 --> 19:35.260
No copying others.

19:35.470 --> 19:37.270
My eyes have in-built plagiarism detectors.

19:39.350 --> 19:39.910
Class is over.

19:46.080 --> 19:47.810
The best part about classes is when they're over.

19:48.080 --> 19:48.940
Goodbye, Ms. Yu.

19:51.310 --> 19:52.150
Ms. Yu.

19:53.380 --> 19:54.750
Let me introduce someone new.

19:54.830 --> 19:56.000
Do you remember the actor

19:56.030 --> 19:56.870
I mentioned?

20:00.070 --> 20:00.990
Hello, Ms. Yu.

20:02.220 --> 20:03.330
Hello, Yu Bofeng.

20:04.370 --> 20:05.710
We've met before.

20:06.190 --> 20:07.250
That's good.

20:07.400 --> 20:08.440
You're not strangers then.

20:08.550 --> 20:10.030
Mr. Yu is taking on

20:10.030 --> 20:11.150
a crime film soon.

20:11.490 --> 20:12.330
Since

20:12.370 --> 20:13.890
you're an expert in this field,

20:14.030 --> 20:14.980
he wants you

20:15.070 --> 20:16.110
to be his consultant

20:16.190 --> 20:17.890
and help him with the role.

20:18.780 --> 20:19.570
Ms. Yu.

20:19.590 --> 20:20.440
Privately,

20:20.500 --> 20:21.350
just teach him

20:21.390 --> 20:22.620
when you're free.

20:22.910 --> 20:23.520
Director Li.

20:23.590 --> 20:25.350
I told you already.

20:25.370 --> 20:26.190
I'm researching

20:25.450 --> 20:29.060
[Serial Murder Case]

20:26.230 --> 20:27.260
a new topic.

20:27.380 --> 20:28.800
I doubt I have time.

20:30.910 --> 20:31.670
Ms. Yu.

20:33.620 --> 20:34.420
He...

20:34.990 --> 20:36.350
His boss, Mr. Wen,

20:36.480 --> 20:37.580
funded a lab

20:37.580 --> 20:38.670
in our school.

20:38.710 --> 20:39.310
Can't you

20:39.350 --> 20:40.390
carve out some time?

20:40.420 --> 20:41.030
Okay?

20:41.070 --> 20:42.270
The principal owes him.

20:42.290 --> 20:43.780
Let him pay it back himself.

20:43.810 --> 20:45.050
What do I have to do with it?

20:46.030 --> 20:46.830
Besides,

20:46.910 --> 20:48.750
I teach here and at a school.

20:48.750 --> 20:49.550
You know that.

20:49.630 --> 20:50.710
I'm swamped.

20:50.820 --> 20:51.750
I can't deal

20:51.770 --> 20:52.710
with a superstar.

20:52.790 --> 20:53.370
No.

20:53.470 --> 20:54.030
Ms. Yu.

20:54.070 --> 20:54.760
Ms. Yu.

20:56.490 --> 20:57.510
I came here

20:57.540 --> 20:59.350
because I really need to learn.

21:00.230 --> 21:01.110
How about this?

21:01.630 --> 21:02.480
I'll just attend

21:02.510 --> 21:03.690
your classes like everyone.

21:04.470 --> 21:04.920
By the way,

21:05.790 --> 21:07.240
this is my first day here.

21:07.990 --> 21:08.870
This is a gift for you.

21:08.890 --> 21:10.030
-No, no, I can’t accept it.
-Don’t worry.

21:10.060 --> 21:10.770
It's not money.

21:10.990 --> 21:11.990
I know you have rules.

21:12.030 --> 21:13.030
This is my...

21:13.790 --> 21:14.590
autographed photo.

21:17.910 --> 21:18.690
Take a look.

21:19.550 --> 21:20.810
It's a souvenir.

21:23.720 --> 21:25.120
I'm not into celebrities. Thanks.

21:28.280 --> 21:28.950
Ms. Yu!

21:33.070 --> 21:33.910
Professor Yu!

21:40.780 --> 21:41.300
I know...

21:41.650 --> 21:43.580
that when you came to my agency

21:43.920 --> 21:45.760
to ask about Wang Qianqian,

21:46.910 --> 21:48.130
I left a bad impression.

21:49.070 --> 21:50.030
But now I have

21:50.070 --> 21:51.510
a role I really want.

21:52.010 --> 21:53.110
I need your professional

21:53.110 --> 21:53.800
help.

21:55.220 --> 21:56.030
Why won't you

21:56.070 --> 21:56.950
teach me?

21:57.820 --> 21:59.040
That's a different matter.

21:59.840 --> 22:01.030
Let's put aside

22:01.030 --> 22:01.990
my impression of you.

22:02.640 --> 22:03.870
I know a bit

22:03.910 --> 22:05.270
about your line of work.

22:05.830 --> 22:07.570
It's just a photo opportunity

22:07.750 --> 22:08.640
so your agency

22:09.310 --> 22:10.910
can promote you

22:10.990 --> 22:13.000
as a hardworking actor,

22:13.110 --> 22:13.760
right?

22:14.390 --> 22:15.110
My classes

22:15.150 --> 22:16.390
are quite serious.

22:17.520 --> 22:18.590
To put it bluntly,

22:18.950 --> 22:19.880
I have no time to

22:19.910 --> 22:20.790
put on a show with you.

22:27.930 --> 22:29.300
-Hello, Ms. Yu.
-Hello, Ms. Yu.

22:41.080 --> 22:42.770
Didn't I tell you?

22:43.010 --> 22:44.470
Knock before entering.

22:45.370 --> 22:46.500
I'll knock next time.

22:50.440 --> 22:51.030
Wait,

22:52.150 --> 22:52.800
shouldn't you

22:52.830 --> 22:53.870
be at the class now?

22:54.720 --> 22:55.730
Don't mention that.

22:55.930 --> 22:56.750
All I got was

22:56.770 --> 22:57.650
a verbal bashing.

23:01.180 --> 23:01.830
Wait.

23:02.420 --> 23:04.360
Did you do it on purpose?

23:05.320 --> 23:06.030
What did I do?

23:07.750 --> 23:08.630
Do you know

23:08.630 --> 23:10.110
who the teacher you found for me was?

23:10.130 --> 23:11.170
It's the female cop

23:11.210 --> 23:12.920
who interrogated me here.

23:15.150 --> 23:16.380
Really? What a coincidence.

23:17.390 --> 23:18.630
I really didn't know.

23:20.320 --> 23:21.300
So,

23:21.390 --> 23:21.990
you might as well

23:22.030 --> 23:23.110
just listen to me

23:23.190 --> 23:24.630
and shoot those two idol dramas.

23:24.880 --> 23:25.610
No way.

23:26.050 --> 23:26.670
Listen.

23:26.670 --> 23:27.970
I must get that role.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.350
I'll do everything

23:29.350 --> 23:30.590
to make her teach me.

23:42.880 --> 23:46.100
[Crayfish]

23:52.640 --> 23:54.350
I'm here. Where are you?

24:12.200 --> 24:13.340
Jiang Chengyi?

24:13.670 --> 24:14.880
Why are you here?

24:14.910 --> 24:15.870
What a coincidence.

24:17.060 --> 24:17.940
Want some food?

24:22.390 --> 24:23.420
I want to ask you something.

24:24.480 --> 24:25.520
Do you know Wang Qiang?

24:28.260 --> 24:28.970
Who?

24:31.140 --> 24:32.900
I... I don't think I know him.

24:33.210 --> 24:35.010
I’m just here for dinner.

24:37.640 --> 24:38.460
Liu Yujie.

24:38.930 --> 24:40.540
Don't take any chances.

24:40.560 --> 24:41.980
Since we're here,

24:42.010 --> 24:43.250
it means we have enough

24:43.270 --> 24:44.140
evidence.

24:44.320 --> 24:45.810
You’d better tell the truth.

24:51.920 --> 24:53.000
Wang Qiang?

24:53.420 --> 24:54.490
I remember now.

24:54.700 --> 24:56.080
He was a classmate...

24:56.990 --> 24:57.880
in middle school.

24:58.080 --> 24:59.800
But he dropped out early.

25:00.350 --> 25:01.660
Since I went to university,

25:01.690 --> 25:03.060
we haven't been in touch.

25:05.470 --> 25:06.940
We've arrested Wang Qiang.

25:07.740 --> 25:08.660
It’s a huge case.

25:08.830 --> 25:10.590
He said he's been in touch with you.

25:10.910 --> 25:11.850
What's that about?

25:12.120 --> 25:13.630
I-I... I don't know.

25:13.840 --> 25:14.760
I didn't do it.

25:15.320 --> 25:16.720
I really don't know anything!

25:16.750 --> 25:17.510
Ding Jing

25:17.510 --> 25:18.590
asked me to contact him.

25:19.640 --> 25:20.410
Ding Jing?

25:23.920 --> 25:25.060
Why did Ding Jing ask you

25:25.080 --> 25:25.800
to contact him?

25:26.310 --> 25:28.250
I... I-I don't know.

25:30.380 --> 25:31.740
Want to talk at the station?

25:32.820 --> 25:33.550
No.

25:34.660 --> 25:35.060
Well,

25:35.080 --> 25:36.730
Wang Qiang and I were classmates.

25:37.110 --> 25:38.580
After he got out of jail,

25:38.810 --> 25:40.050
I-I just...

25:40.150 --> 25:41.580
found a few jobs for him,

25:41.610 --> 25:42.890
but they never lasted.

25:42.930 --> 25:43.810
So I complained

25:43.840 --> 25:45.100
to Jing about this.

25:45.440 --> 25:47.040
Then Jing asked me

25:47.070 --> 25:48.230
to contact him

25:48.510 --> 25:50.410
to ask him for a favor.

25:50.960 --> 25:53.160
Ding Jing asked Wang Qiang for a favor?

25:53.800 --> 25:54.800
What favor?

25:55.170 --> 25:56.040
I really

25:56.060 --> 25:57.230
wasn't aware.

25:57.910 --> 25:58.730
But one time,

25:58.790 --> 26:00.280
when Ding Jing got drunk,

26:00.420 --> 26:01.620
she told me

26:02.190 --> 26:03.210
she...

26:03.890 --> 26:05.150
asked Wang Qiang

26:05.880 --> 26:07.590
to secretly take photos of Lu Yan.

26:13.810 --> 26:15.390
She wants to destroy Lu Yan.

26:17.680 --> 26:19.420
So Ding Jing wants to destroy Lu Yan,

26:19.510 --> 26:21.760
and you helped her find Wang Qiang

26:21.830 --> 26:22.870
to secretly take photos of Lu Yan,

26:22.900 --> 26:23.470
right?

26:23.560 --> 26:24.350
No.

26:24.380 --> 26:25.880
I really don't know anything!

26:25.900 --> 26:27.390
If I knew it was illegal,

26:27.470 --> 26:29.000
how could I've helped her?

26:29.110 --> 26:29.920
Who can prove

26:29.950 --> 26:30.630
your innocence?

26:34.790 --> 26:35.680
Then...

26:35.990 --> 26:36.950
I’ll show you all

26:36.990 --> 26:38.110
my chat histories with Ding Jing

26:38.150 --> 26:39.100
and Wang Qiang.

26:48.260 --> 26:49.460
Make a copy

26:49.490 --> 26:50.710
of her chat histories.

26:50.750 --> 26:51.630
Yes, Captain Jiang.

26:57.150 --> 26:57.870
Do you know

26:57.920 --> 26:59.030
what you're doing?

27:00.300 --> 27:01.970
You're assisting a crime!

27:02.870 --> 27:03.350
I...

27:03.420 --> 27:04.990
Wang Qiang's been arrested.

27:05.020 --> 27:05.770
Do you

27:06.860 --> 27:08.250
want to help us

27:08.460 --> 27:10.160
investigate Ding Jing's crime?

27:10.410 --> 27:11.240
Yes.

27:11.480 --> 27:13.320
I'll cooperate fully.

27:13.610 --> 27:14.820
My colleague will

27:15.470 --> 27:16.840
tell you what to do later.

27:17.790 --> 27:18.360
Okay.

27:18.800 --> 27:19.780
One more thing.

27:21.490 --> 27:23.420
Did Ding Jing hire someone to disguise

27:23.450 --> 27:24.050
as Deng Man?

27:26.790 --> 27:27.670
I don't know.

27:28.310 --> 27:30.290
Ding Jing never mentioned that.

27:32.040 --> 27:32.700
Okay.

27:33.080 --> 27:34.840
Take her back to the station for a testimony.

27:40.880 --> 27:45.010
[No parking in front of the warehouse]

27:45.230 --> 27:45.910
Captain Jiang.

27:46.040 --> 27:47.310
Should we just interrogate Ding Jing?

27:49.300 --> 27:49.980
No, not yet.

27:52.070 --> 27:53.080
Jiang Chengyi.

27:53.110 --> 27:54.030
Our families are having dinner

27:54.070 --> 27:55.270
the day after tomorrow.

27:55.550 --> 27:56.890
Can you come pick me up?

27:57.660 --> 28:00.790
[Outpatient]

28:01.030 --> 28:02.060
Xiaoman, it's late.

28:02.110 --> 28:02.710
Time to sleep.

28:02.710 --> 28:03.970
No!

28:04.030 --> 28:04.440
Xiaoman.

28:04.470 --> 28:05.430
Stop making a fuss.

28:05.490 --> 28:06.510
I don't want to.

28:08.300 --> 28:08.870
I don't want to.

28:08.870 --> 28:10.240
It's very late, Xiaoman.

28:10.350 --> 28:11.750
I don't want the operation!

28:11.780 --> 28:13.190
Xiaoman, you're not a baby anymore.

28:13.210 --> 28:14.210
-You can’t do this.
-No!

28:14.310 --> 28:15.190
Xiaoman!

28:15.310 --> 28:16.060
I don't want to!

28:16.100 --> 28:17.180
Listen to me.

28:17.200 --> 28:18.480
You'll be fine after the operation.

28:18.510 --> 28:19.270
I don't want to.

28:19.290 --> 28:19.840
-Xiaoman!
-Xiaoman.

28:19.880 --> 28:20.720
I don't want to!

28:21.030 --> 28:21.600
Xiaoman?

28:24.420 --> 28:25.610
Dr. Lu.

28:25.740 --> 28:27.680
What's wrong? In a bad mood?

28:28.910 --> 28:30.070
Well...

28:30.300 --> 28:31.860
do you want a gift?

28:32.110 --> 28:32.550
Yes.

28:32.610 --> 28:33.430
Yes?

28:33.710 --> 28:34.110
Okay.

28:34.350 --> 28:35.310
Then...

28:35.640 --> 28:36.890
guess which hand it's in.

28:41.260 --> 28:42.320
This one.

28:42.360 --> 28:43.020
This one?

28:43.050 --> 28:44.010
Are you sure?

28:44.150 --> 28:44.790
Yes.

28:44.810 --> 28:45.400
Okay.

28:47.710 --> 28:48.510
Chocolate.

28:48.550 --> 28:49.630
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

28:49.630 --> 28:50.350
You're welcome.

28:50.390 --> 28:51.710
Try it. See if you like it.

28:52.550 --> 28:53.980
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

28:54.150 --> 28:55.010
It's no problem.

28:55.040 --> 28:56.070
Will the operation

28:56.150 --> 28:57.580
put Xiaoman in any danger?

28:57.710 --> 28:58.550
Don't worry.

28:58.630 --> 28:59.390
It'll be fine.

28:59.550 --> 29:00.790
And all of his

29:00.830 --> 29:02.260
indicators are normal.

29:02.430 --> 29:03.920
The operation can proceed as scheduled.

29:04.270 --> 29:04.910
That's good.

29:04.990 --> 29:05.890
After the operation,

29:05.990 --> 29:06.670
does it mean

29:06.670 --> 29:07.670
he'll recover?

29:09.000 --> 29:10.410
Just let him rest well.

29:11.380 --> 29:12.450
Thank you.

29:13.120 --> 29:13.880
Xiaoman.

29:14.560 --> 29:16.150
Look at what's in this hand.

29:16.680 --> 29:18.480
Is it also chocolate?

29:18.560 --> 29:19.760
It's also chocolate.

29:20.430 --> 29:21.290
You're so smart.

29:21.790 --> 29:22.730
Thank you.

29:22.990 --> 29:24.110
You're welcome.

29:24.780 --> 29:25.690
Have a good rest.

29:25.880 --> 29:26.620
Be good.

29:26.830 --> 29:27.300
Okay.

29:27.530 --> 29:28.320
I'll get going.

29:28.350 --> 29:29.190
Sorry for the trouble.

29:29.190 --> 29:29.640
It's nothing.

29:29.820 --> 29:30.380
Bye.

29:30.550 --> 29:31.030
Bye.

30:10.880 --> 30:11.600
Lu Yan.

30:22.290 --> 30:23.460
Wen.

30:23.530 --> 30:27.190
[Medical expertise conquers intractable diseases
Medical ethics spread across borders]

30:23.880 --> 30:24.840
Why are you here?

30:27.310 --> 30:34.480
[Exemplary in both ethics and expertise, with compassion for patients]

30:29.790 --> 30:31.040
Yu Bofeng's brand endorsement

30:31.070 --> 30:32.800
has a mixer on Friday night.

30:32.980 --> 30:33.550
Come have fun.

30:34.610 --> 30:38.980
[Boya Porcelain]

30:36.390 --> 30:38.030
Boya Porcelain...

30:39.040 --> 30:40.760
Ding Jing?

30:42.220 --> 30:43.330
They're the organizer.

30:44.750 --> 30:45.470
You go ahead.

30:45.500 --> 30:46.420
I'll pass.

30:46.550 --> 30:47.990
I have many operations lately.

30:48.030 --> 30:48.640
I'm super busy.

30:50.110 --> 30:51.240
I was thinking,

30:51.260 --> 30:52.870
if you have time,

30:53.270 --> 30:54.040
you can have fun

30:54.070 --> 30:54.840
to relax.

30:54.780 --> 31:00.200
[Medical expertise conquers intractable diseases
Medical ethics spread across borders]

30:55.160 --> 30:55.880
Oh, right,

30:56.030 --> 30:56.760
Tang Jie

30:56.790 --> 30:57.770
and the others will be there.

30:58.320 --> 30:59.310
We old classmates

30:59.340 --> 31:00.070
can gather again.

31:01.470 --> 31:02.770
Tang Jie is rich,

31:02.830 --> 31:03.650
and you're a boss.

31:03.750 --> 31:05.580
I have to clock in at work.

31:05.820 --> 31:06.820
Go ahead without me.

31:08.480 --> 31:09.170
Okay, then.

31:09.320 --> 31:10.260
If you change your mind,

31:10.260 --> 31:10.790
let me know.

31:13.620 --> 31:14.380
Wen.

31:14.420 --> 31:17.870
[Exemplary in both ethics and expertise, with compassion for patients]

31:14.650 --> 31:15.960
You couldn't have came

31:15.990 --> 31:17.640
all the way here just to send me an invitation.

31:20.250 --> 31:21.460
What if I say I did?

31:28.030 --> 31:29.080
I'm just kidding.

31:29.560 --> 31:30.920
I read a script recently.

31:30.950 --> 31:32.460
The male lead said this.

31:32.480 --> 31:33.560
I'm just trying it out.

31:35.640 --> 31:37.000
I-I still prefer your

31:37.030 --> 31:38.520
original way of speaking.

31:40.170 --> 31:41.410
Actually, I came

31:41.590 --> 31:42.890
to have dinner with Dr. Han.

31:42.960 --> 31:44.040
I'm getting help from his manpower,

31:44.070 --> 31:44.980
so I should thank him.

31:45.870 --> 31:46.840
Go along then.

31:46.870 --> 31:47.590
When

31:47.630 --> 31:48.760
your script is done,

31:48.790 --> 31:49.910
you can show it to me.

31:50.040 --> 31:50.570
Okay.

31:51.390 --> 31:52.460
Tell me if you change your mind.

32:01.350 --> 32:05.020
[Invitation]

32:22.760 --> 32:24.470
[Dressed up for some Western food!]

32:25.160 --> 32:28.200
[Pure Realm Western Restaurant
No. 3 of Ninghai City Western Restaurants]

32:42.110 --> 32:42.830
Uncle, Auntie.

32:42.870 --> 32:44.750
My friend just sent me this tea.

32:44.810 --> 32:46.490
They all say it's very good.

32:46.530 --> 32:47.550
Try it out and let me know

32:47.550 --> 32:48.690
how it tastes.

32:49.020 --> 32:50.390
Thank you, Jing.

32:50.410 --> 32:52.290
Seriously, Jing is so

32:52.470 --> 32:53.920
meticulous and considerate.

32:53.990 --> 32:54.590
Like how

32:54.620 --> 32:56.070
she always manages to find

32:56.100 --> 32:57.520
all these nice restaurants

32:57.550 --> 32:58.720
that are all unique

32:58.740 --> 32:59.640
to treat us

32:59.670 --> 33:00.670
to dinner every time.

33:00.870 --> 33:01.950
You've really got

33:02.030 --> 33:02.760
a great kid.

33:02.790 --> 33:03.900
She's praising you.

33:04.060 --> 33:05.470
If you're satisfied,

33:05.510 --> 33:07.160
then I didn't waste my efforts.

33:07.510 --> 33:08.120
I love it!

33:08.500 --> 33:09.110
Ding.

33:09.640 --> 33:10.750
This is too luxurious.

33:10.770 --> 33:11.870
You ordered so many dishes.

33:11.890 --> 33:13.120
How can we finish them?

33:13.270 --> 33:14.870
How is this too luxurious?

33:14.950 --> 33:15.500
You two

33:15.550 --> 33:17.080
always doted on me.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.430
Nothing's too luxurious for you.

33:18.470 --> 33:19.030
Exactly.

33:19.310 --> 33:19.890
Look.

33:20.070 --> 33:21.070
She's right.

33:21.110 --> 33:22.470
Nothing's too luxurious for you.

33:22.980 --> 33:23.660
Look.

33:23.950 --> 33:24.920
Jing and Jiang

33:24.990 --> 33:25.880
have known each other for so long.

33:25.910 --> 33:26.910
We're practically

33:27.030 --> 33:27.670
family.

33:27.700 --> 33:28.580
Yes, yes.

33:28.760 --> 33:30.870
They're true childhood friends.

33:33.340 --> 33:34.680
Why isn't Jiang here yet?

33:34.960 --> 33:36.650
Mom, he’s busy with work.

33:36.710 --> 33:37.190
But I

33:37.230 --> 33:38.000
just texted him.

33:38.030 --> 33:38.990
He’s on his way.

33:40.000 --> 33:41.060
Jiang's so

33:41.090 --> 33:42.390
preoccupied with work.

33:42.460 --> 33:44.330
But in other aspects,

33:44.450 --> 33:46.130
the clock is ticking.

33:46.960 --> 33:47.820
That kid

33:47.880 --> 33:49.040
doesn't think

33:49.190 --> 33:49.830
that far.

33:50.310 --> 33:51.640
Our kids are all grown up.

33:51.770 --> 33:53.280
They have their own

33:53.350 --> 33:54.990
ideas and plans for their future.

33:55.020 --> 33:56.510
We can't intervene.

33:56.550 --> 33:57.870
It's not for us to decide, right?

33:57.990 --> 33:58.560
Yes, yes.

33:58.670 --> 33:59.440
-Respect them.
-We can't intervene.

33:59.470 --> 34:00.510
We can't intervene.

34:02.370 --> 34:03.400
Yes, yes.

34:03.460 --> 34:05.320
That’s true, in theory.

34:05.560 --> 34:06.390
Jiang

34:06.420 --> 34:07.770
is a sensible kid.

34:07.820 --> 34:08.590
He never

34:08.590 --> 34:09.920
wants you to worry.

34:10.449 --> 34:12.150
But marriage is a big deal.

34:12.179 --> 34:13.699
As parents,

34:13.830 --> 34:15.449
we can't leave it up to them.

34:15.570 --> 34:17.300
We have to pay attention.

34:17.590 --> 34:19.350
We have to know everything

34:19.429 --> 34:20.699
to rest assured.

34:20.770 --> 34:22.510
What my mom said really makes sense.

34:22.550 --> 34:23.270
Many of my friends

34:23.290 --> 34:24.929
ended up marrying an old classmate.

34:24.949 --> 34:26.440
They told me it's called,

34:26.469 --> 34:28.219
"New is not always better, especially for people."

34:28.270 --> 34:29.909
That's how we all think now.

34:30.830 --> 34:31.940
Youngsters nowadays

34:31.960 --> 34:32.739
a-a-are...

34:32.980 --> 34:34.639
So traditional, huh?

34:34.659 --> 34:36.590
This is called going back to the basics.

34:38.100 --> 34:39.100
Has Wang Qiang fessed up?

34:39.170 --> 34:40.199
He's still insisting

34:40.320 --> 34:41.159
he's acting

34:41.190 --> 34:42.110
on his own.

34:42.520 --> 34:43.440
And the other?

34:44.400 --> 34:45.610
I just questioned Qin Yue.

34:45.710 --> 34:46.350
He said Ding Jing

34:46.350 --> 34:47.730
hasn't called Liu Yujie.

34:47.790 --> 34:48.350
Okay.

34:48.400 --> 34:49.030
Keep an eye on it.

34:49.150 --> 34:49.590
Yes.

34:49.830 --> 34:50.280
Okay.

34:51.960 --> 34:53.620
That's right, this kid...

34:53.790 --> 34:54.810
Uncle, Auntie.

34:54.870 --> 34:55.560
Dad, Mom.

34:55.630 --> 34:55.960
He's here.

34:55.960 --> 34:56.989
I'm really sorry.

34:57.070 --> 34:57.910
I'm late because

34:57.910 --> 34:58.480
of work.

34:59.230 --> 35:00.190
You're finally here.

35:00.270 --> 35:00.830
Have a seat.

35:00.830 --> 35:01.270
Okay.

35:01.340 --> 35:02.690
You always come so late.

35:02.750 --> 35:03.230
Okay.

35:03.270 --> 35:03.950
Yeah.

35:04.030 --> 35:04.750
Sit now.

35:04.790 --> 35:05.990
The elders all had to wait for you.

35:06.710 --> 35:07.430
It's okay.

35:07.550 --> 35:08.830
He's busy at work.

35:08.850 --> 35:09.400
Come on.

35:09.510 --> 35:09.910
Here.

35:09.930 --> 35:10.790
Have a seat, Jiang.

35:12.250 --> 35:12.900
Ding.

35:13.380 --> 35:14.030
All right.

35:14.190 --> 35:15.550
Our families are all seated.

35:15.670 --> 35:16.700
Then let's

35:16.950 --> 35:17.550
dig in.

35:17.630 --> 35:18.030
Okay, okay.

35:18.110 --> 35:18.510
Come on!

35:18.550 --> 35:18.910
Come on.

35:18.990 --> 35:19.710
Cheers!

35:19.920 --> 35:20.590
Come on!

35:20.610 --> 35:21.010
Here.

35:21.090 --> 35:21.670
From now on,

35:21.750 --> 35:23.180
we should gather more often.

35:23.270 --> 35:24.560
We can't go so long

35:24.590 --> 35:25.270
without meeting.

35:25.270 --> 35:25.750
Yeah.

35:25.800 --> 35:26.710
Sure, no problem.

35:26.730 --> 35:27.970
I'll find more restaurants.

35:28.190 --> 35:28.740
Come on.

35:33.170 --> 35:34.370
-Jiang, eat up.
-Eat more.

35:34.430 --> 35:35.150
Yeah, I’ll do it myself.

35:35.150 --> 35:35.550
Try it.

35:35.630 --> 35:36.830
I ordered all your favorite dishes.

35:36.830 --> 35:37.910
Here, cheers.

35:37.930 --> 35:39.260
Mom, eat more.

35:39.760 --> 35:40.710
Have more meat.

35:41.300 --> 35:42.700
I know you like it.

35:43.770 --> 35:44.800
Uncle, Auntie,

35:44.920 --> 35:45.670
my company is

35:45.710 --> 35:47.270
holding an art mixer in a few days.

35:47.310 --> 35:48.120
I'd like to

35:48.150 --> 35:49.150
invite you two to guide me.

35:50.660 --> 35:52.560
That is youngsters' stuff.

35:52.610 --> 35:53.720
We're too old.

35:53.750 --> 35:55.040
We won't get involved.

35:55.160 --> 35:56.350
We can't understand it anyway.

35:56.350 --> 35:57.470
Who said you're old?

35:57.590 --> 35:58.760
Ask a stranger.

35:58.870 --> 36:00.090
If I didn't know you,

36:00.430 --> 36:01.910
I'd assume you were around...

36:02.020 --> 36:02.720
40 years old.

36:03.290 --> 36:04.220
Look at her.

36:04.310 --> 36:05.210
Such a sweet talker.

36:05.390 --> 36:06.160
Your invitation.

36:06.270 --> 36:06.940
Here, here.

36:06.990 --> 36:08.320
That made you really happy, huh?

36:08.470 --> 36:09.080
Auntie.

36:09.110 --> 36:09.920
You must come.

36:09.950 --> 36:10.390
Thank you.

36:10.470 --> 36:11.190
I'll be there.

36:11.540 --> 36:12.980
Boya Porcelain.

36:14.470 --> 36:15.390
I'm busy with work.

36:15.390 --> 36:16.270
I don't have time.

36:16.820 --> 36:17.630
Make time.

36:17.630 --> 36:18.960
Just take it!

36:19.590 --> 36:20.440
How are you so busy?

36:20.470 --> 36:21.030
Take it.

36:21.230 --> 36:21.660
Okay.

36:21.750 --> 36:23.310
I'll go experience some art

36:23.370 --> 36:24.220
and enrich myself.

36:24.310 --> 36:25.230
I'll keep it for you

36:25.550 --> 36:26.290
with ours.

36:29.710 --> 36:30.590
How's

36:31.200 --> 36:32.480
your health been lately?

36:33.660 --> 36:35.300
Not bad. Average.

36:35.390 --> 36:36.550
There are no problems

36:36.630 --> 36:37.510
in my medical checkups.

36:37.670 --> 36:39.160
Good, that's good.

36:39.780 --> 36:40.420
Come on.

36:40.680 --> 36:41.780
Come on.

36:41.800 --> 36:42.580
Here.

36:43.190 --> 36:43.670
Here.

36:45.980 --> 36:46.970
She...

36:48.140 --> 36:49.420
asked Wang Qiang

36:50.360 --> 36:52.060
to secretly take photos of Lu Yan.

36:53.160 --> 36:54.470
She wants to destroy Lu Yan.

37:02.410 --> 37:03.990
I know a great shop.

37:04.030 --> 37:04.720
Sure.

37:04.760 --> 37:05.400
Take me there.

37:05.400 --> 37:05.710
Yeah.

37:05.790 --> 37:06.310
Auntie Ding.

37:06.330 --> 37:07.090
Jiang never takes me.

37:07.190 --> 37:07.670
Uncle.

37:08.100 --> 37:08.710
Um...

37:08.830 --> 37:09.990
why don't you go back first?

37:10.070 --> 37:11.880
I'll chat with Ding Jing a bit.

37:12.940 --> 37:13.550
Okay.

37:13.550 --> 37:13.950
You guys talk.

37:13.950 --> 37:14.790
Go home first.

37:14.810 --> 37:15.360
Let's go.

37:15.670 --> 37:16.340
Okay.

37:16.590 --> 37:17.010
Here.

37:17.070 --> 37:17.580
I'm leaving.

37:17.600 --> 37:17.920
Bye.

37:17.950 --> 37:18.350
Bye.

37:18.790 --> 37:19.560
Go back.

37:20.410 --> 37:20.910
Come on.

37:24.810 --> 37:25.670
What's the matter?

37:26.260 --> 37:27.780
Thank you for today.

37:28.340 --> 37:29.270
Why are you suddenly

37:29.310 --> 37:30.190
so polite?

37:32.780 --> 37:33.630
Um...

37:34.030 --> 37:35.570
have you met Lu Yan lately?

37:37.510 --> 37:38.590
Why'd I meet her?

37:38.630 --> 37:39.590
We're not close.

37:43.100 --> 37:44.800
There's something strange.

37:46.210 --> 37:47.560
A while ago,

37:48.190 --> 37:49.810
Lu Yan and I met Deng Man.

37:50.960 --> 37:51.800
Deng Man?

37:52.580 --> 37:53.670
Isn't she dead?

37:54.510 --> 37:55.140
Yeah.

37:55.270 --> 37:56.480
That's why it's strange.

37:57.360 --> 37:58.410
Are you too tired from work

37:58.440 --> 37:59.730
that you're seeing things?

38:00.030 --> 38:00.970
Nonsense.

38:01.030 --> 38:02.280
It's impossible.

38:05.360 --> 38:05.970
Nothing.

38:05.990 --> 38:06.840
I was just asking.

38:06.900 --> 38:08.730
A lot has happened lately.

38:09.420 --> 38:11.500
You... should be careful too.

38:11.860 --> 38:13.000
Don't go out often.

38:14.420 --> 38:15.190
Take this back.

38:15.220 --> 38:16.380
I really don't have time.

38:18.910 --> 38:21.500
[Boya Porcelain]

38:21.980 --> 38:22.890
What do you mean?

38:23.460 --> 38:24.160
Jiang Chengyi.

38:24.920 --> 38:26.030
Rejecting me again?

38:26.880 --> 38:28.260
How many times have you

38:28.310 --> 38:29.820
rejected me since university?

38:30.710 --> 38:31.730
Have you ever considered

38:31.790 --> 38:32.910
that I'm a girl too,

38:32.950 --> 38:34.190
with feelings and pride?

38:34.230 --> 38:35.020
Throughout these years,

38:35.050 --> 38:36.670
again and again!

38:39.090 --> 38:40.190
It's out of

38:40.640 --> 38:41.380
respect

38:41.400 --> 38:42.190
that I always

38:42.210 --> 38:43.440
make things clear.

38:43.690 --> 38:51.990
[Boya Porcelain]

38:43.760 --> 38:45.050
We're just friends;

38:45.170 --> 38:45.890
childhood friends

38:46.070 --> 38:46.650
and classmates.

38:46.680 --> 38:47.870
Nothing else,

38:47.890 --> 38:48.510
right?

38:50.390 --> 38:51.320
Still just friends

38:51.350 --> 38:52.100
and childhood friends?

38:54.080 --> 38:55.440
I thought that over the years,

38:55.470 --> 38:56.430
if I tried harder,

38:56.470 --> 38:57.430
loved you more,

38:57.430 --> 38:58.590
and persisted more,

38:58.630 --> 39:00.230
you'll finally notice me!

39:01.440 --> 39:02.530
Ms. Ding.

39:03.070 --> 39:04.630
Why don't you just

39:04.670 --> 39:05.500
buy one?

39:05.550 --> 39:06.700
Why bother knitting it?

39:06.790 --> 39:07.710
It's so much work.

39:07.770 --> 39:09.200
How are they the same?

39:09.310 --> 39:10.250
This is my sincerity.

39:10.350 --> 39:11.740
It can't be bought.

39:14.840 --> 39:15.640
Jiang Chengyi!

39:15.880 --> 39:16.880
Happy birthday.

39:17.200 --> 39:18.050
Thank you.

39:18.070 --> 39:19.210
I knitted it myself.

39:19.250 --> 39:19.910
Look.

39:19.930 --> 39:21.550
It's my first time doing such a thing.

39:22.600 --> 39:23.960
T-This is too precious.

39:23.990 --> 39:24.830
I can't accept it.

39:24.870 --> 39:25.920
But I'll accept your blessing,

39:26.030 --> 39:26.660
okay?

39:26.680 --> 39:27.790
Is it because

39:27.830 --> 39:28.670
you have

39:28.710 --> 39:29.610
a girlfriend?

39:29.640 --> 39:30.850
What does it have to do with that?

39:31.890 --> 39:32.710
Since you don't

39:32.710 --> 39:33.670
have a girlfriend,

39:33.740 --> 39:34.870
give me a chance.

39:34.890 --> 39:35.940
I like you.

39:36.300 --> 39:38.030
Ding Jing, this again?

39:38.070 --> 39:39.150
We're childhood friends

39:39.180 --> 39:40.220
and buddies.

39:40.260 --> 39:40.990
Quit messing around.

39:41.140 --> 39:42.160
I'm not.

39:42.310 --> 39:43.420
I'm serious.

39:43.470 --> 39:45.060
Can't you tell after all these years?

39:45.150 --> 39:46.650
I've always liked you a lot.

39:47.210 --> 39:47.990
It's because of you

39:48.030 --> 39:49.270
that I chose Ninghai University.

39:49.300 --> 39:50.910
I was planning to go abroad.

39:51.030 --> 39:52.610
It's weird. We grew up together.

39:52.670 --> 39:53.630
Quit it already.

39:53.710 --> 39:54.790
What kind of girl do you like?

39:54.790 --> 39:55.670
I'll change for you.

39:55.830 --> 39:56.430
Don't change.

39:56.460 --> 39:57.440
You're good now.

39:58.190 --> 39:59.040
If you change,

39:59.070 --> 40:00.130
we can't be friends anymore.

40:00.270 --> 40:00.710
No.

40:00.710 --> 40:02.000
Look, I'm changing.

40:02.030 --> 40:02.320
You...

40:02.320 --> 40:03.310
D-Don't change.

40:03.390 --> 40:04.150
Bye.

40:04.310 --> 40:05.830
I'm serious!

40:05.990 --> 40:07.430
I really like you!

40:13.970 --> 40:15.250
It's because of

40:15.370 --> 40:17.050
that damn Lu Yan, right?

40:19.350 --> 40:20.980
What does it have to do with her?

40:21.020 --> 40:22.240
Why are you insulting her?

40:23.540 --> 40:24.480
Then why'd you

40:24.510 --> 40:25.620
do this to me?

40:26.130 --> 40:27.390
Do you know

40:27.430 --> 40:28.660
how popular I am?

40:28.670 --> 40:30.790
I've been waiting for you for so long!

40:34.900 --> 40:36.400
Stop denying it.

40:38.620 --> 40:39.020
Fine.

40:40.230 --> 40:41.480
It's because of her.

40:41.830 --> 40:42.510
And?

40:44.030 --> 40:46.250
Then she must die!

40:49.880 --> 40:51.340
You should watch your words.

40:51.950 --> 40:53.190
If anything

40:53.410 --> 40:54.740
happens to Lu Yan,

40:55.510 --> 40:56.970
you're the prime suspect.

41:22.200 --> 41:26.400
[Somerset Serviced Apartment]

42:06.230 --> 42:06.970
Ding Jing.

42:14.660 --> 42:15.510
Are you crazy?

42:15.550 --> 42:16.350
Why're you following me?

42:16.850 --> 42:17.580
Let's talk.

42:18.180 --> 42:19.770
What's there to talk about?

42:20.050 --> 42:20.770
Deng Man.

42:20.910 --> 42:22.770
What did you do to her eight years ago?

42:24.270 --> 42:25.070
What Deng Man?

42:25.090 --> 42:25.620
I don't know her.

42:25.650 --> 42:26.860
You don't know her?

42:27.340 --> 42:28.820
Then why do her photos and hairpin

42:28.840 --> 42:29.320
trigger

42:29.350 --> 42:30.100
you?

42:33.120 --> 42:34.690
You did that crap?

42:37.060 --> 42:37.840
Ding Jing.

42:38.910 --> 42:39.910
Listen up.

42:40.230 --> 42:41.720
If you don't admit it,

42:41.950 --> 42:43.460
I'll pester you

42:43.760 --> 42:45.160
until you admit it.

42:45.500 --> 42:46.320
Lu Yan.

42:46.750 --> 42:48.390
Stop playing tricks.

42:48.750 --> 42:49.840
What do you know?

42:50.040 --> 42:51.120
If you really know,

42:51.150 --> 42:52.230
just call the police.

42:52.430 --> 42:53.870
Why're you following me?

42:59.030 --> 43:00.150
I have evidence.

43:00.400 --> 43:01.840
I’ll ask Jiang Chengyi

43:01.860 --> 43:02.960
to see if these can prove

43:02.990 --> 43:04.000
you killed Deng Man.

43:09.040 --> 43:09.870
Don't talk nonsense

43:09.910 --> 43:10.960
to Jiang Chengyi!

43:11.110 --> 43:12.040
Lu Yan, stop!

43:14.890 --> 43:16.030
Evidence?

43:16.640 --> 43:17.290
Evidence?

43:17.330 --> 43:19.080
I asked you to get the evidence...

43:19.810 --> 43:21.280
Evidence, right?

43:21.310 --> 43:22.880
Evidence! Evidence!

43:24.250 --> 43:25.630
You want evidence, right?

43:26.910 --> 43:27.720
Stop looking.

43:27.790 --> 43:28.470
Don't waste time.

43:28.470 --> 43:29.830
I'll just tell you.

43:30.840 --> 43:32.170
I bullied her.

43:32.290 --> 43:33.300
What's wrong?

43:33.520 --> 43:34.540
She washed my clothes

43:34.590 --> 43:35.110
and shoes

43:35.110 --> 43:36.230
and even knelt down to me!

43:36.690 --> 43:38.000
That's because she's timid,

43:38.070 --> 43:38.700
useless,

43:38.750 --> 43:39.590
and weak!

43:39.610 --> 43:40.640
It's not my fault.

43:44.560 --> 43:46.070
I'll ask you one last time.

43:47.480 --> 43:48.440
Did you

43:49.360 --> 43:50.780
force Deng Man to her death?

43:53.610 --> 43:55.700
Let me tell you one last time too.

43:56.330 --> 43:58.050
Her death has nothing to do with me.

43:58.760 --> 44:00.870
She asked for it.

44:04.100 --> 44:04.910
Lu Yan.

44:05.710 --> 44:06.560
Have you ever

44:06.590 --> 44:08.050
considered that you're a jinx?

44:09.030 --> 44:10.030
Why does everyone

44:10.070 --> 44:11.750
around you have a tragic ending?

44:16.950 --> 44:18.340
I think

44:18.480 --> 44:20.230
if it were up to me,

44:20.570 --> 44:22.330
your death would solve everything.

44:48.820 --> 44:49.770
Wen.

44:50.350 --> 44:51.820
About the art mixer,

44:52.520 --> 44:53.310
I'm going.

45:00.950 --> 45:04.940
[Professor Yu]

45:05.470 --> 45:06.500
What’s wrong, Captain Jiang?

45:06.600 --> 45:07.290
Professor Yu.

45:07.680 --> 45:08.820
Are you free tomorrow?

45:08.970 --> 45:10.090
I need to talk to you.

45:10.160 --> 45:11.230
Okay, see you tomorrow.
